## 📊 Project Overview

This is **Human Problem Solver System (HPSS)** – a full-stack platform where users post real problems and get solutions from experts, with AI assistance. Think of it as a marketplace for advice and consultation.

### **Core Features:**
- **Problems & Solutions** – Users post problems, experts offer solutions
- **Expert Consultations** – Book 1-on-1 calls with verified experts  
- **AI Matching** – AI categorizes problems and suggests the right experts
- **Trust System** – Reputation scores, voting, expert verification badges
- **Real-time Notifications** – Users stay updated on interactions
- **Admin Dashboard** – Moderate content, manage platform

---

## **🏗️ Architecture**

**Frontend (Next.js)**
- Modern React app with dark mode support
- Pages: Dashboard, Ask Problems, Browse Experts, Consultations, Notifications
- Tailwind CSS for styling

**Backend (Express.js)**
- REST API with 9 feature modules:
  - `/auth` – Login/signup
  - users – User profiles
  - `/problems` – Problem CRUD
  - `/experts` – Expert profiles
  - `/consultations` – Booking system
  - `/ai` – AI recommendations
  - `/categories` – Problem categories
  - `/notifications` – Real-time updates
  - `/reports` – Content moderation

**Database (PostgreSQL)**
- Prisma ORM for type-safe queries
- Includes migrations and seed data

**Infrastructure**
- Docker Compose for local development
- Nginx reverse proxy for production
- Rate limiting & security headers

